title: Should we implement LIP-2?
body:
Overview: Introducing a new asset to be bonded, take the top 5 by ranking into consideration for assets that can be bonded. 

The introduction of bonds is be signaled by their ranking and discussions within our discord. You can attribute your voting power between multiple choices. 

Low-ranked choices can be put to a vote again at a later date.

- Toke (Tokemak)
- gOHM (Olympus DAO)
- CVX (Convex Finance)
- YFI (Yearn Finance)
- ALCX (Alchemix)
- sSpell (Abracadabra Money)
- RBN (Ribbon Finance)
- Aave (AAVE Lending Protocol)
- SDT/xSDT (Stake DAO)
- xPremia (Premia Finance)
- Sushi/xSushi (SushiSwap)
- LDO (Lido Staking)
- Rune/xRune (Thorchain)
- Luna (Terra)
- Index (Indexed Coop)
- Anchor (Anchor Protocol)

Authors: exalted, heaume, IceCube

Discussion: https://forum.lobis.finance/d/16-request-for-new-bond-assets
Formal Proposal Link: https://forum.lobis.finance/d/19-lip-2-new-bond-assets
